snippet.title: The Weeknd Takes the Stage in Fortnite Festival
snippet.description:
Diamond certified and award-winning artist The Weeknd lands in Fortnite Festival, a brand-new music experience launching in Fortnite, on December 9.

Download Fortnite now and get ready to perform & jam with your favorite tracks at: https://www.fortnite.com/download

#TheWeeknd #Fortnite #FNFestival
